/* How to send an email with SMTP to two recipients: Alice (alice@example.com) and Bob (bob@example.org). The email subject is 'Meeting Reminder' and the body content is 'This is a reminder for our meeting scheduled tomorrow at 10 AM.' */
mail.smtp.send
   message
      to
         .
            name:Alice
            email:alice@example.com
      to
         .
            name:Bob
            email:bob@example.org
      subject:Meeting Reminder
      entity:text/plain
         content:This is a reminder for our meeting scheduled tomorrow at 10 AM.